CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 14, 1959, pg. B6 reads: "Ivy Leafers - The Charming young Ivy Leafers (pledge club of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority) above, were pinned at the home of Soror Lois Jeanne Dougan, last week, in impressive ritual. Tip-toe with anticipation, the eight young misses received  the cherished acknowledgement from the Greeks.  in pictured are Ivy Leafers Annette McCance, Norma Magee, Winifred Haddock, Connie Cottingham, Patricia Marlow, Dorothy Gloster, Frances Pace and Sara Blakey. - Harris Photo.'
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority Ivy Leaf pledge club members, including Annette McCants, Norma Nixon, Winifred "Winnie" Haddock, Constance "Connie" Cottingham, Patricia Marlow, Dorothy Gloster, Frances Pace, and Sarah Blakey, posed in home of Lois Jeanne Dougan
